搜索数据库的关键词:
1. 疾病+机理模型
("chikungunya" OR "CHIKV") AND
("mathematical model" OR "transmission dynamics" OR "SEIR" OR "vector-host" OR "Ross-Macdonald")

2. 疾病+预测/时空
("chikungunya" OR "CHIKV") AND
("forecast*" OR "prediction" OR "spatiotemporal" OR "Bayesian" OR "spatial model" OR "Rt")

3. 疾病+环境/媒介
("chikungunya" OR "Aedes-borne arbovirus") AND
("temperature" OR "rainfall" OR "climate" OR "vector population" OR "Aedes aegypti" OR "Aedes albopictus")

4. 相似病种迁移
("dengue" OR "zika" OR "arbovirus") AND
("spatiotemporal model" OR "Bayesian hierarchical model" OR "forecasting" OR "vector dynamics")
